## Workflow Naming Convention
Format: `WF: [Agent Purpose] - [Specific Function]`
Examples:
- `WF: Blog Master - AI Content Pipeline`
- `WF: WordPress Pages - ACF Content Generator`
- `WF: Podcast Producer - Content Pipeline`

## Error Handling Strategy
1. All nodes set to `"onError": "continueRegularOutput"`
2. Slack notifications on failures
3. Airtable status updates on errors
4. No workflow should completely fail - partial execution is OK

## Testing Protocol
- Always test on inactive copy first
- Verify credentials before activation
- Check Airtable connections
- Test webhook URLs
- Validate context7 memory keys
